text gText_TheStorySoFar_TheCriminalUnderbelly {
    format("The SanFran criminal underbelly, using agents within the prison, staged a prison riot. The agents took guards hostage, and demanded that the government turn the island over to the prisoners. This occupation lasted for years, and the demands of the prisoners grew more unreasonable as time went on.")
